Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 志溫姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:19:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,生日禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,可 可以打開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,當然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,雨傘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 志溫姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,和大蔥一模一樣 很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,大蔥…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,車站前在派發的 我就收下了
